items.preText:
Bit of a hold-up in play. Asghar is talking to the umpires, with Mujeeb also there. Mujeeb seems to be having some pain in his leg. And he's limping off. Luckily for Afghanistan, he's bowled out his full quota.

Tazz: "The game is still 50/50. Bangladesh is so unpredictable. From 165/5 they can end up below 200 all out. So, until Bangladesh decides to do what they are able to deliver, we can't predict anything. "


Last ten overs now. Bangladesh have done well to recover from that middle-order wobble. If they can get about 80 in the last ten, they'll fancy their chances for sure.
